                <h1>The Prophet Malachi: A Messenger of God</h1>
                <p>Malachi is the last prophet in the Old Testament, known for his prophetic book, which addresses the spiritual decline of Israel. His name means "my messenger," and he called for the people's return to faithfulness to God, emphasizing the importance of true worship, justice, and the coming of the Lord.</p>
